CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 7, 1963, pg. 22 reads: "The Champion Vikings - Kneeling: Cora Simpson, Beacia Webb, Cecelia Howard and Dolores Simpson. Standing: Janet Kendricks, Daisy Pettis, Lynn Redman, Nellie Simpkins, holding the trophy, Manager Lewis Turner; Wilma Cargile, Ernestine Banks, Elizabeth Ivey and Elaine Crowell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Vikings softball team, kneeling from left: Cora Simpson, Beacia Webb, Cecelia Howard, Dolores Simpson; standing: Janet Kendricks, Daisy Pettis, Lynn Redman, Nellie Simpkins, manager Lewis Turner holding trophy, Wilma Cargile, Ernestine Banks, Elizabeth Ivey, and Elaine Crowell, on Kennard Field
